   Heard on the Street:
   Some See New Energy in Oil Refiners' Stocks,
   Figuring Firms' Properties Will Rise in Value
   ----
   By David B. Hilder
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/06/90
</DATE>
